==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Dehors
<hw>De*hors"</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Mil.)</fld> <def>All sorts of
outworks in general, at a distance from the main works; any advanced
works for protection or cover.</def> <rj><au>Farrow.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dehort</ent>⟦br⟧
